pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: methods.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: R. Heller
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - customstyle.css
  toc: true
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  description-meta: R. Heller's personal website.
  title-block-banner: true
  theme:
    light: flatly
    dark: darkly
  title: Entscheidungsbaum
  listing:
    contents: methods/**/*.qmd
    sort: date desc
    type: default
    categories: true
    sort-ui: true
    filter-ui: true
    fields:
      - date
      - title
      - reading-time
      - description
      - categories
    feed: true
  page-layout: full
